Covid19_Taiwan = Table.read_table(' Taiwan CDC  - .csv')
Covid19_Taiwan = Covid19_Taiwan.drop('CDC  URL').drop('').drop('').drop('').drop('').drop('Unnamed: 13').drop('').drop('')

Covid19_cases = Covid19_Taiwan.group(['', ''])
Covid19_cases_domestic = Covid19_cases.where('', are.equal_to(''))
Covid19_cases_imported = Covid19_cases.where('', are.equal_to(''))
Covid19_cases_others = Covid19_cases.where('', are.not_equal_to('')).where('', are.not_equal_to(''))
Covid19_death = Covid19_Taiwan.group('')

date = pd.date_range('20200101', periods = 110)

Covid19_Taiwan_cases = Table().with_columns(
    'Date', date.date,
    'Domestic', np.zeros(110),
    'Imported', np.zeros(110),
    'Others', np.zeros(110),
    'Death', np.zeros(110)
)

for i in range(Covid19_Taiwan_cases.num_rows):
    Covid19_Taiwan_cases.column('Date')[i] = str(Covid19_Taiwan_cases.column('Date').item(i))

for i in range(Covid19_Taiwan_cases.num_rows):
    for j in range(Covid19_cases_domestic.num_rows):
        if Covid19_Taiwan_cases.column('Date').item(i) == Covid19_cases_domestic.column('').item(j):
            Covid19_Taiwan_cases.column('Domestic')[i] = Covid19_cases_domestic.column('count').item(j)
            
for i in range(Covid19_Taiwan_cases.num_rows):
    for j in range(Covid19_cases_imported.num_rows):
        if Covid19_Taiwan_cases.column('Date').item(i) == Covid19_cases_imported.column('').item(j):
            Covid19_Taiwan_cases.column('Imported')[i] = Covid19_cases_imported.column('count').item(j)
            
for i in range(Covid19_Taiwan_cases.num_rows):
    for j in range(Covid19_cases_others.num_rows):
        if Covid19_Taiwan_cases.column('Date').item(i) == Covid19_cases_others.column('').item(j):
            Covid19_Taiwan_cases.column('Others')[i] = Covid19_cases_others.column('count').item(j)
            
for i in range(Covid19_Taiwan_cases.num_rows):
    for j in range(Covid19_death.num_rows):
        if Covid19_Taiwan_cases.column('Date').item(i) == Covid19_death.column('').item(j):
            Covid19_Taiwan_cases.column('Death')[i] = Covid19_death.column('count').item(j)
            
Covid19_Taiwan_cases.show(5)

1.2. Basic Comparsion and Analysis¶

1.2.1. Comparsion of infected cases based on age and gender¶
In [50]:
Covid19_age_gender = Table().with_columns(
    '', Covid19_weekly.column(''),
    '', Covid19_weekly.column(''),
    '', Covid19_weekly.column('')
)
Covid19_age_m = Covid19_age_gender.where('', are.equal_to('M'))
for i in range(len(Covid19_age_m.column(1))):
    if Covid19_age_m.column(1).item(i) == '4':
        Covid19_age_m.column(1)[i] = '00-04'
    elif Covid19_age_m.column(1).item(i) == '5-9':
        Covid19_age_m.column(1)[i] = '05-09'
Covid19_age_m = Covid19_age_m.group('')

Covid19_age_f = Covid19_age_gender.where('', are.equal_to('F'))
for i in range(len(Covid19_age_f.column(1))):
    if Covid19_age_f.column(1).item(i) == '4':
        Covid19_age_f.column(1)[i] = '00-04'
    elif Covid19_age_f.column(1).item(i) == '5-9':
        Covid19_age_f.column(1)[i] = '05-09'
Covid19_age_f = Covid19_age_f.group('')        
Covid19_age_f = Table().with_columns(
    '', np.append('00-04', Covid19_age_f.column(0)),
    'count', np.append(0, Covid19_age_f.column(1))
)

Covid19_age_gender_result = Covid19_age_m.join('', Covid19_age_f, '').relabel('', 'AGE').relabel('count', 'Male').relabel('count_2', 'Female')
Covid19_age_gender_result = Covid19_age_gender_result.sort('AGE', descending = True).barh(0,height = 4)
